Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:08.19,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,500)}「難道是試膽大會！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到小楓的郵件說是大家來放煙花的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己卻不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  琴音沒和你在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她早我兩個小時出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像帶了很多東西的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來那個包裹裡好像有長髮的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,長髮是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  這是小楓的留言？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  是不是發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就分成兩組去找琴音和小楓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  抽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是試膽大會！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,試膽大會啊  好久沒玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  好可怕啊春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在一起就不會有事的  小優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吻…吻我一下或許就不會害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  我也是黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  春香那是橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  怎麼看都是黃色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思  我不能和小優在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要相同顏色的組一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶  我是黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小雫  我們一組了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這反應是什麼情況啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  我是隊友你不滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小柚感覺完全不會害怕的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事故感不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好可怕～～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  沒有感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是優還真是對不住了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小優  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  我們一起吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小柚～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是進行了交換
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那春香你們10分鐘後跟來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還來得及回頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在耍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香你也只有現在能說說風涼話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真要有什麼情況我可不救你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  我隨口說說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分鐘後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尾隨而來的美月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優這孩子  居然這麼晚還到這種地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  果然和春香同學在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還好平時在頭飾上塗了螢光塗料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來這地方還真讓人不怎麼舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能害怕  想點什麼開心的事再尾隨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開心的事…  開心的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長  張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能是春香同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會想起春香同學啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…春香  剛剛有沒有看到什麼東西在閃光？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出現啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊  小優
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別把我扔下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  一下子就傳出了悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是…看到了什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優  你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什麼東西跟過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  要是跟到這裡來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吻…吻我一下或許就不會害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定真會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  小優…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  吻我一下或許就不會害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被看穿了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  居然這麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說怪物也是小楓或者琴音的其中一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  春香…快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心中有什麼東西覺醒了的春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我平靜下來以前  請一直吻著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我一定要讓你平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優  你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優？優  你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在叫我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  優
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是跟在你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們為什麼會抱在一起啊  給我分開！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之姐姐  趕緊從這裡出去比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才就在被人喊著名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別嚇唬你姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是春香同學一邊喊著優的名字一邊在接吻嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有喊名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你整天就這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別走散了  一起行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:13.50,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,注：投懷送抱之後的左擁右抱之姐妹丼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必了  我就一個人回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟春香同學靠那麼近  我的心臟受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕就害怕了  不用不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三個人在一起就不會害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是這麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就當作是這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,再注：順理成章之姐妹丼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  優  好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,試膽大會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒說是試膽大會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說了來放煙花的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還搞抽籤什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  似乎多了個不該存在的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是想搞試膽大會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只準備了煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,試膽大會明年再弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好不容易做了些簽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得不抽太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那跟在我後面叫我名字的是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼  別說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就只做了煙花的準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學真是個體貼的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.88,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,710)\fs45}「難道是試膽大會！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.88,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,710)\fs45}「難道是試膽大會！？」
