Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小柚你喜歡甜的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜歡炒麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然炒麵我也很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是在海邊小店吃的炒麵最棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜歡杯面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.36,0:23:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炒麵麵包也超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.98,0:24:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫！？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  Trick 5
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「和姐姐一起喝茶吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和「魔女與蘋果與姐姐」這兩篇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊？！
